Class Invoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • Invoice

  • public class Invoice
extends java.lang.Object
    This Invoice class contains all the attributes and methods regarding the creation of an Invoice. The Invoice class interacts with the Cart and the Transaction classes to create an invoice object. The Invoice class is responsible for the following: - invoiceNum: int - date: Date - orderNum: int - email: String - address: String - shipped: boolean Note that this class does not directly interact with the PurchaseOrder class or the Lot class.
    Author:
    Vezorla
